## Original xv6 Acknowledgements

xv6 is inspired by John Lions's Commentary on UNIX 6th Edition.
See https://pdos.csail.mit.edu/6.1810/ for the original project.

Original authors: Russ Cox, Frans Kaashoek, Robert Morris (MIT PDOS).

For the full list of contributors to the original xv6 project,
see the original README at https://github.com/mit-pdos/xv6-riscv.

